1
00:00:09,809 --> 00:00:11,044
I'm terminating my contract.

2
00:00:11,578 --> 00:00:12,612
Terminating?

3
00:00:13,713 --> 00:00:14,581
I knew there was something

4
00:00:14,582 --> 00:00:15,822
going on with you and Bai Xing.

5
00:00:16,549 --> 00:00:17,589
Let me tell you right now,

6
00:00:18,018 --> 00:00:19,018
I'm not allowing it.

7
00:00:19,586 --> 00:00:20,786
I'm not asking for permission.

8
00:00:23,757 --> 00:00:25,190
According to your contract,

9
00:00:25,191 --> 00:00:26,431
you still have eighteen months.

10
00:00:27,727 --> 00:00:28,995
There's nothing to discuss.

11
00:00:30,830 --> 00:00:32,098
Nothing to discuss, huh?

12
00:00:32,632 --> 00:00:34,167
Then don't blame me when I bench you.

13
00:00:34,567 --> 00:00:35,567
I'll ruin him.

14
00:00:39,272 --> 00:00:40,272
What's this?

15
00:00:40,874 --> 00:00:41,775
Evidence of all the side deals

16
00:00:41,776 --> 00:00:44,009
you've made over the years.

17
00:00:44,010 --> 00:00:45,078
It's a significant amount.

18
00:00:45,545 --> 00:00:46,879
If I show this to the boss,

19
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:47,881
you're finished here.

20
00:00:52,652 --> 00:00:54,053
You broke into my computer?

21
00:00:54,054 --> 00:00:55,354
I didn't have to break in.

22
00:00:55,355 --> 00:00:56,723
I just hacked it.

23
00:00:58,091 --> 00:00:59,091
Look,

24
00:01:00,427 --> 00:01:01,194
you know I only got into this

25
00:01:01,195 --> 00:01:02,862
because of one person.

26
00:01:03,396 --> 00:01:05,031
And that person is Bai Xing.

27
00:01:05,732 --> 00:01:06,399
Just look the other way

28
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:07,933
and pretend you don't know.

29
00:01:07,934 --> 00:01:09,469
I'll keep making you money.

30
00:01:10,170 --> 00:01:11,303
It's not worth it.

31
00:01:11,304 --> 00:01:14,874
Don't throw your career
away for some B-list celebrity.

32
00:01:29,889 --> 00:01:31,224
Hei Mingyan.
